{"tid":1816824,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[傾計App] HowsYourDate [有得Send 相啦] [8]","createTime":"2020-01-08T14:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T09:46:34.000Z","uid":61239,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5a76b88721b7e8637227aa3ebc5fd4bfd6e77803","tid":1816824,"uid":61239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聖誕快樂 希望已經成功出pool既用戶們開心過聖誕<br />\n就算未成功既都唔好氣餒，現實追女仔難，app入面更難，但絕對係一個好既平台認識多d朋友<br />\n<br />\n特別提醒：<br />\n請勿性擾騷男／女性user，封鎖帳號之後唔會解鎖<br />\n<br />\n黎緊新版本：<br />\n1. Delete Message<br />\n2. 網頁版<br />\n<br />\nFeature: <br />\n<br />\n- 每日只可以抽一個異性出黎傾計，或者等人地抽你出黎 (必定係12小時曾經登入過既人)<br />\n<br />\n- 限時圖片(5秒)，如果對方cap圖，會收到通知<br />\n<br />\n- 為公平起見，每人每日只會被配對2～4次<br />\n<br />\n- 可以抽同性朋友，亦都可以防止同性朋友抽到自己<br />\n<br />\n- 如果覺得太多人搵，可以開啟防止打擾功能，唔會再有人match到你<br />\n<br />\n- App 有內置頭像，無得上傳自己頭像，玩之前請準備好中伏既心態<br />\n<br />\n- 唔洗任何相／facebook，只需要你既名，年齡，地區 就可以註冊到帳號<br />\n<br />\n- 無voice message<br />\n<br />\n- 每日可以更新你果一日既心情，希望增加話題之餘，亦都可以俾對方多d關心自己<br />\n<br />\n- 一開始唔建議大家交換相，希望大家傾左計了解下，當識多個朋友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIOS 傳送門： <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/howsyourdate/id1381389467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fhowsyourdate%2Fid1381389467&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=c34c1b4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/howsyourdate/id1381389467</a><br />\n<br />\nANDROID 傳送門： <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.howsyourdate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.howsyourdate&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=5f0f3da9\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.howsyourdate</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家有時間可以係app store／google play俾個5* 我地<br />\n如果有咩需要admin 協助，可以telegram 我： howsyourdate_official<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開發緊新app：<br />\n1. 心事app<br />\n2. 飲食app <br />\n如果有咩合作機會可以隨時搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舊post(1)： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/781047/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/781047/page/1</a><br />\n舊post(2)： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/835665/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/835665/page/1</a><br />\n舊post(3)： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/883230/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/883230/page/1</a><br />\n舊post(4)： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/897274/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/897274/page/1</a><br />\n舊post(5)： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/911351/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/911351/page/1</a><br />\n舊post(6)： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/926003/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/926003/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"78575b16792144aee34e4d1baf13e76717b645f9","tid":1816824,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:29:36.000Z","msg":"變左sales+毒撚肥婆app"},{"pid":"5f28f8828fca145aa6d1fb178a8558f41a08ec1b","tid":1816824,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78575b16792144aee34e4d1baf13e76717b645f9","tid":1816824,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:29:36.000Z","msg":"變左sales+毒撚肥婆app"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"又係毒步巴你"},{"pid":"2803a1c6e89432bc763e7a272e6585a41218a4c6","tid":1816824,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"快啲